Name:                kansas-comet
Version:             0.1
Synopsis:            A javascript push mechanism and event listener
Homepage:            https://github.com/kufpg/kansas-comet/
Bug-reports:         https://github.com/kufpg/kansas-comet/
License:             BSD3
License-file:        LICENSE
Author:              Andrew Gill <andygill@ku.edu>, Andrew Farmer <anfarmer@ku.edu>
Maintainer:          Andrew Gill <andygill@ku.edu>
Copyright:           (c) 2012 The University of Kansas
Category:            Web
Stability:           experimental
Build-type:          Simple
